13 A. The Louisiana Department of Health and any managed care entity
14 administering Medicaid behavioral health services shall not require
15 cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) or first aid certification for behavioral
16 health staff as a condition of provider enrollment, staff credentialing, or
